<p>The <a href="http://hapijs.com/api#server" rel="nofollow"><strong>hapi.js</strong></a> documentation is not <em>especially</em> (<em>complete</em>) beginner-friendly<sup>1</sup> ...</p>  <p>What is the <em>distinction</em> between a Server Auth <a href="http://hapijs.com/api#serverauthschemename-scheme" rel="nofollow"><strong><em>Scheme</em></strong></a> and <a href="http://hapijs.com/api#serverauthstrategyname-scheme-mode-options" rel="nofollow"><strong><em>Strategy</em></strong></a>? </p>  <p>Do we need to have <em>both</em>?</p>  <p><sup>1</sup>If someone can <em>explain</em> the difference we will PR into the docs.</p>  <p>Also posted on: <a href="https://github.com/hapijs/discuss/issues/163" rel="nofollow">https://github.com/hapijs/discuss/issues/163</a></p>